snippet.title: Shah Rukh Khan Joins the KKR Dressing Room Awards after Final | #KnightsTV | TATA IPL 2024
snippet.description:
After an unforgettable evening of triumph, CEO Venky Mysore honours the champion players of Kolkata Knight Riders (KKR) as they clinch the TATA IPL Trophy for the third time! Watch as the stars of KKR bask in the glory of victory, their hard work and dedication recognized with prestigious awards. Mitchell Starc, Vaibhav Arora, Harshit Rana, Andre Russell, Sunil Narine, Varun Chakaravarthy and all our Knights were applauded in the dressing room. 

But the celebrations don't end there! Witness a heartwarming moment as Shah Rukh Khan, the beloved Co-owner of KKR, receives a special award from CEO Venky Mysore himself. He thanks King Khan for his support and love for the team. SRK's passion for cricket shines as he graces the #TATAIPL2024Final at Chepauk in Chennai, and now joins the celebrations too.

snippet.title: 2nd T20I | Highlights | Pakistan Tour Of England | 25th May 2024
snippet.description:
In the 2nd T20I of the Pakistan Tour Of England, the hosts set a target of 183, with Jos Buttler's scintillating 84 runs off 51 balls leading the charge. Shaheen Afridi's impressive bowling, with 3 wickets at an economy of 9, kept Pakistan in the contest. However, England's bowlers, spearheaded by Reece Topley who also claimed 3 wickets, managed to restrict Pakistan to 160 runs. Despite Fakhar Zaman's explosive 45 runs off 21 balls, Pakistan fell short by 23 runs.
.

Shiddat Digitally Presented by PEL

Asra, a beautiful and cherished young woman, has led a life filled with love and care from her family. In contrast, Sultan, a determined and charismatic perfectionist, overcomes the challenges of his troubled childhood to consistently achieve his desires.

Despite their stark personality differences, Asra falls in love with Sultan. However, after they marry, Asra realizes that Sultan is not the ideal man she had envisioned. To please him, she sacrifices her desires and undergoes a significant transformation.

This revelation becomes the catalyst for an unending series of problems between them. The journey through marital life becomes a complex maze as Asra and Sultan attempt to navigate challenges, each trying to mold the other according to their own will and preference.

Will Asra and Sultan change for each other, or will the growing list of problems between them persist? When Asra discovers the reality about Sultan, how will she react? Is Sultan contemplating leaving Asra? Can love overcome all obstacles, or are some differences too profound to bridge?

Asra, a beautiful and cherished young woman, has led a life filled with love and care from her family. In contrast, Sultan, a determined and charismatic perfectionist, overcomes the challenges of his troubled childhood to consistently achieve his desires.

Despite their stark personality differences, Asra falls in love with Sultan. However, after they marry, Asra realizes that Sultan is not the ideal man she had envisioned. To please him, she sacrifices her desires and undergoes a significant transformation.

This revelation becomes the catalyst for an unending series of problems between them. The journey through marital life becomes a complex maze as Asra and Sultan attempt to navigate challenges, each trying to mold the other according to their own will and preference.

Will Asra and Sultan change for each other, or will the growing list of problems between them persist? When Asra discovers the reality about Sultan, how will she react? Is Sultan contemplating leaving Asra? Can love overcome all obstacles, or are some differences too profound to bridge?

snippet.description:
‚òûKUDI HARYANE VAL DI / CHORI HARYANE AALI (Trailer) Ammy Virk| Sonam Bajwa |Ajay Hooda | 14th June
#kudiharyanevaldi #newpunjabimovie  #newpunjabimovietrailer #ammyvirk #sonambajwa #ajayhooda #latestmovietrailers  #choriharyanedi #komalchaudhary #rajmawar #yograjsingh #latestpunjabimovietrailer
#movietrailer2024 

Get ready for a cinematic treat of the coming together of the JATT & JAATNI (Ammy Virk & Sonam Bajwa), with the official trailer of 'KUDI HARYANE VAL DI' / ‚ÄòCHORI HARYANE AALI‚Äô releasing worldwide in cinemas on 14th June 2024!!

Presented by Ramara Films, written and directed by Rakesh Dhawan (Writer of Honsla Rakh & Chal Mera Putt, Director of Aaja Mexico Chaliye), produced by Pawan Gill, Aman Gill, Sunny Gill (Producers of Shadaa & Puaada)

This is a fun comedy, cross-cultural Punjabi-Haryanvi romance entertainer, about a loveable Punjabi Jatt (Ammy Virk) who crosses paths with the lively Haryanvi Jaatni (Sonam Bajwa). It‚Äôs love at first sight for this desi Jatt, who once didn‚Äôt care for anything associated with his family legacy of wrestling but will now go to any lengths to prove his love for the game to impress his lady love, but will this be enough? 

Cast: Ammy Virk, Sonam Bajwa, Ajay Hooda, Yograj Singh, Yashpal Sharma, Hardeep Gill, Honey Mattu, Seema Kaushal, Mahabir Bhullar, Deedar Gill, Manpreet Dolly, Mintu Kapa etc

Nosherwan Ghaznavi, a wealthy young man, faces a pivotal moment in his life after his brother's death. This film was Written, Edited, Music composed, Lyrics, Directed & Produced by Bandi Saroj Kumar, under his banner #BSKmainstream.

snippet.title: Soni Soni | Ishq Vishk Rebound | Rohit Saraf, Pashmina| @DarshanRavalDZ@jonitamusic, Rochak,Gurpreet
snippet.description:
"Soni Soni" is the ultimate anthem for dance lovers blending irresistible beats with heartfelt lyrics. Perfectly crafted for Gen Z, this track promises to get you moving and feeling the love. Get ready to vibe and groove to your new favorite hit! from the much-awaited movie "Ishq Vishk Rebound." Starring the charming Rohit Saraf and the beautiful Pashmina Roshan, and the mesmerizing voices of Darshan Raval, Jonita Gandhi & Rochak Kohli, this track is set to steal hearts. Lyrics Penned By Gurpreet Saini With music by the talented Rochak Kohli, this track promises a perfect blend of love and melody. Don't miss it!

Stay updated with the latest videos from Tips Official, Subscribe on the below link.
http://youtube.com/tipsofficial

In Theatres From 21st June 2024

Song Details :
Song Name: Soni Soni 
Singers: Darshan Raval, Jonita Gandhi & Rochak Kohli
Music Director: Rochak Kohli
Music Producer: Sharan Rawat
Lyricist: Gurpreet Saini
Choreographer: Vijay Ganguly
Director of Photography (Song): Debojeet Ray
Mix and Master by Shadab Rayeen @ New Edge
Assistant Engineers: Pukhraj & Anup

Movie Details : 
Producers- Ramesh Taurani and Jaya Taurani
Director- Nipun Avinash Dharmadhikari
Lead Cast- Rohit Saraf, Pashmina Roshan, Jibraan Khan, Naila Grrewal
Secondary Cast- Kusha Kapila, Supriya Pilgaonkar, Akarsh Khurana, Shilpa Vishal Shetty, Shataf Figar, Anita Kulkarni and Sheeba Chadda 
Story and Screenplay writers- Dr. Vinay Chhawal, Vaishali Kamalakar Naik, and Ketan Pedgaonkar
Additional Screenplay writers- Akarsh Khurana and Nipun Avinash Dharmadhikari
Dialogue writer- Akarsh Khurana & Lisha Bajaj
Director of Photography- Milind Jog
Audiography & Sound Design- Anirban Sengupta
Music- Rochak Kohli 
Lyrics- Gurpreet Saini, Kumaar and Gautam G Sharma
Choreographer- Vijay Ganguly
Editor- Chandan Arora
Production Designer- Nikhil Kovale
Costume Designers- Abhilasha Devnani & Manisha Melwani

Music On Tips Music (Tips Industries Ltd.)

Ki Karan
Meri Baat Maane Na

Kitna Tenu Chahe 
Tenu Aaye 
Meri Yaad Na

Kehna Tenu Kehna
Ik Tu Hi 
Bas Pyaar Hai Mera

Koi Nahi Tere Pehle
